Saw #Dhurandhar today. Exceptional is the word. Easily the best Indian ever film in this genre.<br/><br/>The tight edits, parallel high octane events and the music .... All top class.<br/><br/>The attention to detail; the story line that depicts the long arc of real world espionage and what it takes to achieve it..... the craft is evident in the fact that even at end of 3:30 hrs, yeh audience was wanting more.<br/><br/>Great work
@AdityaDharFilms
and team.
